INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','product_display','0','75','75','und','0','<p>Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','product_display','0','76','76','und','0','<p>Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','article','0','86','86','und','0','<p>This is Edvile.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','93','93','und','0','<p>Hi guys, we are Daphné and Edward, we live in Belgium and we work our asses off. But finally we realized that life isn''t only about&nbsp;work. So we found the time, came up with&nbsp;a plan and&nbsp;packed the bags to do this 6-weeks-long&nbsp;amazing trip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tomorrow we are leaving for&nbsp;our road trip from Canada, through West Coast of US and all the way down to Mexico! We are very excited to expand our minds,&nbsp;discover the nature,&nbsp;find inspiration in different cultures and&nbsp;explore new cities. We are up for an adventure&nbsp;and we will live in a simple way.&nbsp;Back to basics!&nbsp;We won''t travel alone, our friend, Jelle, will join us in Brussels. My brother, Jonathan, aka ''johny true love'' will also join us in Vancouver, Canada. He''s already living, traveling and working&nbsp;in Canada for one year. He will show us the best spots of Vancouver, Vancouver Island and&nbsp;Rocky Mountains. They both will share this experience with us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This blog is a little experiment. We want to make it&nbsp;fun, for you and for us,&nbsp;but we''ll see how it goes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>XX Edward en Daphné</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','95','95','und','0','<p>Flying to&nbsp;our first destination,&nbsp;Vancouver,&nbsp;we had to make two stops in Montreal and Ottawa. With every stop we went back in time, the sun was still shining and it was still the afternoon... &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After 22 hours of traveling we finally arrived at the other side of the world. It felt like it was an endless day. Strange, but a wonderful feeling!</p>\r\n','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','blog','0','96','96','und','0','<p>We took a ferry to Vancouver Island and couldn’t believe the spectacular scenery.&nbsp;On our way there we made two stops in Ucluelet aka ''Ukee''. We couldn’t resist a walk in the rain forest, with crazy high trees, wild rivers, fresh air and this all in early spring colours. We took a break on the rocks at the&nbsp;river and got overwhelmed by such&nbsp;enormous&nbsp;force of nature. We started jumping from rock to rock, playfully, just like kids. But the closer we got to the river the more overpowered we felt by its magnificence.&nbsp;We ended our day with an incredible view of&nbsp;sunset over the sea and great Gin&amp;Tonic in our hands.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In one day we had so many different experiences/adventures, that it is still hard to believe. WOW!</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','98','98','und','0','<p>The city of mountains and sea...&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On our first night in Vancouver we didn’t get much sleep because of the jetlag. At 5 AM we jumped out off bed wide awake. Because of&nbsp;excitement we didn''t feel tired at all.&nbsp;We did a city walk in beautiful Vancouver and got a breakfast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','99','99','und','0','<p>It''s a picture day today! Smile!</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','100','100','und','0','<p>The Great Bear Rainforest is&nbsp;a national park that protects part of the only temperate rain forest in the world.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','101','101','und','0','<p>Such a beauty!</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','102','102','und','0','<p>According to Wikipedia Ucluelet means "people of the safe harbour" in the indigenous&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nuu-chah-nulth_language" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;" title="Nuu-chah-nulth language">Nuu-chah-nulth</a>&nbsp;(Nootka) language.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','blog','0','103','103','und','0','<p>Kennedy Lake is the largest lake on&nbsp;Vancouver Island.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','105','105','und','0','<p>Riding a whale, even though is was&nbsp;a fake one, was pretty awesome.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','106','106','und','0','<p>The view from our bed..</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','107','107','und','0','<p>Exhausted, but still very excited.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','109','109','und','0','<p>From Vancouver Island we went on a little boat trip to see the whales. We had the rain, we had the sun, we had still waters of the Pacific Ocean all around us and the big curling waves. We felt so small, but still in harmony with the nature.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We saw cute sea lions, eagles and an eagle nest, in the open sea on the rocks, just between two little islands. And of course we saw the whales! They were so beautiful and we felt very grateful! We saw their tails and the backs and their spectacular spouts.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unfortunately we don''t have the pictures of that moment, but we have memories of it. Later on we gonna post some videos of the spouts and our wonderful experience on the boat trip.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','110','110','und','0','<p>We slept in our car on our way to the Rocky Mountains. It was very cold, but romantic, especially with the view like this.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','111','111','und','0','<p>On our way to the Rocky Mountains we couldn’t resist to make a stop at the lake for a breakfast.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','112','112','und','0','<p>:)</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','113','113','und','0','<p>First impressions of Rocky M.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','114','114','und','0','<p>You can find a lot of driftwood on the coastline. The wood looks so beautifull, it''s very inspiring. It coult be&nbsp;used to make some nice furniture.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','blog','0','115','115','und','0','<p>The Rainforest of VC Island holds some giant trees. Storms cruched a lot of trees, now they make place for new kinds of growth.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','116','116','und','0','<p>Driving trough a residential neiberhoud we spotted some deer in someones garden. Here this is like normal, but for us it was pretty funny. Actually they are looking for safety and refuge from wolves and cougars. That''s why they prefer to stay in town</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','117','117','und','0','<p>This place goes in the our list of the most beautifull cost lines&nbsp;on earth. It''s where the rainforest kisses the ocean.&nbsp;We did a long walk following the pacific rim trail. No words, simply amazing...</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','118','118','und','0','<p>You have to imagine Canada has a lot of trees. While driving to the rockies we passed like millions and millions of trees. It''s dificult to explain how big and expanded this erea is.&nbsp;As one of the smallest countries, Belgium,&nbsp;to visit the second largest country, Canada, it is difficult to grasp the wideness of the nature&nbsp;and the endless&nbsp;wilderness. The erea is breathtaking to drive trough. One of the most beautifull scenic&nbsp;routes, infusing the eye with yet another postcard view turn after turn. It''s hard&nbsp;to capture this feeling on photo or film, you have to try it sometime!</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','119','119','und','0','<p>It seems we lost our trail while hiking in the rocky mountains on the bald one. Afterward we could laugh, but a little further we got a little scared.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','120','120','und','0','<p>While waiting for our whale watching boat trip to depart we spotted some sea lions in the harbor. They seemed to be very hungry.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','121','121','und','0','<p>If you pay good attention you can see the sprouts of the whales.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','blog','0','122','122','und','0','<p>Spotted the steller sea lion grouping together at a small island.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','123','123','und','0','<p>Amazing view from the boat.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','124','124','und','0','<p>Breathtaking Rockies...</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','125','125','und','0','<p>Canada</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','126','126','und','0','<p>Canada</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','127','127','und','0','<p>When drivin to the usa we suddenly passes this amazing house build by a woodcarver.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','128','128','und','0','<p>On our way we spotted a lot of cool&nbsp;houses.&nbsp;The style of building is totally different than what we''re used to back home.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','129','129','und','0','<p>Our morningview after a night camping in the wild...</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','130','130','und','0','<p>Portland is one of a kind, the people here call it the wierd city. For us it could feels more like a home. The people are friendly and help each other out in the many communities that the city holds. There are only 500 000 people in Portland, so here it''s considered a small city. There are lot''s of flowers and people decorate the streets, many old and cool industrial buildings and a special food culture vibe with loads of cool bars, restaurants and food trucks.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','131','131','und','0','<p>ADX is a colaborative makersplace where individuals and organizations make and learn.By working together and&nbsp;sharing tools, knowledge&nbsp;and experience.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','132','132','und','0','<p>Thank you Justin for the nice stay in your home!</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','133','133','und','0','<p>Mmmmm</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','blog','0','134','134','und','0','<p>Made ourselves&nbsp;a nice sandwich on&nbsp;the road.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html');
